Accommodation

    Airbnb - Used a lot by digital nomads, very good especially when booking a month or more stay.
    Nomad Rental - Specific for Nomads
    Hostelworld - Budget accommodation for nomads that prefer a more social environment or need to keep costs down.
    Couchsurfing - For staying one or few nights in a new city, last minute arrangements, usually free. Good for meeting locals
    Coliving - For living with other nomads or people with similar interests.
    Booking - lots of filters, different types of accomodation, good prices and choices. 
    Agoda  - Best for Southeast Asia.


